{"word":"G2008 - ἐπιτιμάω - epitimáō - ep-ee-tee-mah'-o - Charge","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιτιμάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epitimáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-tee-mah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Charge</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அதட்டு, கடிந்து கொள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to show honor to, to honor"},{"paragraph":"2. to raise the price of"},{"paragraph":"3. to adjudge, award"},{"paragraph":"4. to tax with fault, rate, chide, rebuke, reprove, censure severely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5091 - τιμάω - timáō - tim-ah'-o/5091\">G5091</a>; to <i>tax upon</i>, that is, <i>censure</i> or <i>admonish</i>; by implication <i>forbid:</i> - (straitly) charge, rebuke.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2008/2008\">G2008</a>, <a href=\"#/G2009/2009\">G2009</a>"}]}